  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001961.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) When I , Lipit-Eštar , the humble shepherd of Nibru , the true farmer of Urim , ceaseless provider of Eridug , the en priest suitable for Unug , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the favourite of Inana , established justice in Sumer and Akkad , then I built the E-niĝsisa at Namkarum , the supreme place of the gods ."
    }
  ],
